                            <comment id="17632694" author="olegk" created="Sat, 12 Nov 2022 16:00:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=chen2&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;chen2&quot;&gt;chen2&lt;/a&gt; I think HttpClient is correct in rejecting *.compute-1.amazonaws.com subject as being too broad. I added more test cases to document present assumptions about correct behavior:&lt;/p&gt;

